ptolemy.data.type.test

Class TestToken

  • java.lang.Object
    • ptolemy.data.Token
      • ptolemy.data.type.test.TestToken

  • public class TestToken
extends Token
    This is a new type of token. It is used to test the TypeLattice to ensure that unspecified token types are allowed, and simply made incomparable to everything else.
    Since:
    Ptolemy II 2.0
    Author:
    Steve Neuendorffer
    Pt.AcceptedRating:
    Red (neuendor)
    Pt.ProposedRating:
    Red (neuendor)
